"title": "5081: Adam, creation and life of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5081: adam, creation and life of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Adam is portrayed as the height of God's creation, made in the image and likeness of God, and entrusted with the stewardship of creation.</p>\n<h2>The creation of Adam</h2>\n<h3>As a unique event</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:7\">GEN 2:7</a></strong></p>\n<h3>In the image of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:26-Gen1:27\">GEN 1:26–1:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:1\">GEN 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:7\">1CO 11:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:9\">JAS 3:9</a></p>\n<h3>His commission from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:28\">GEN 1:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:15\">GEN 2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:26\">GEN 1:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:4-Ps8:8\">PSA 8:4–8:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:14-Ps115:16\">PSA 115:14–115:16</a></p>\n<h3>His incompleteness without Eve</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:18-Gen2:24\">GEN 2:18–2:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:27\">GEN 1:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:1-Gen5:2\">GEN 5:1–5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:4-Matt19:6\">MAT 19:4–19:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:6-Mark10:9\">MRK 10:6–10:9</a></p>\n<h3>His position and privileges</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:28-Gen1:29\">GEN 1:28–1:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:19-Gen2:20\">GEN 2:19–2:20</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The limitations of his freedom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:16-Gen2:17\">GEN 2:16–2:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1-Gen3:3\">GEN 3:1–3:3</a></p>\n<h2>The fall of Adam</h2>\n<h3>The nature of his sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:6\">GEN 3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:16-Gen2:17\">GEN 2:16–2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:12\">GEN 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:17\">GEN 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:7\">HOS 6:7</a></p>\n<h3>Immediate results of his sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:7-Gen3:10\">GEN 3:7–3:10</a></strong></p>\n<h3>God's curse upon Adam and the earth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:17-Gen3:19\">GEN 3:17–3:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:29\">GEN 5:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:1\">JOB 7:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:9\">JOB 10:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:3\">PSA 90:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:17-Eccl2:23\">ECC 2:17–2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:20\">ECC 3:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:20\">ROM 8:20</a></p>\n<h2>The life of Adam after the fall</h2>\n<h3>His expulsion from the garden</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:21-Gen3:24\">GEN 3:21–3:24</a></p>\n<h3>His children</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:1-Gen4:2\">GEN 4:1–4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:25\">GEN 4:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:3-Gen5:4\">GEN 5:3–5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr1:1\">1CH 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>His lifespan and death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:5\">GEN 5:5</a></strong></p>",
